      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This vehicle is the perfect canvas for a DIY enthusiast or mechanic! While it's currently in poor condition and will require some significant mechanical work and cosmetic TLC to get back to its best, it offers a great opportunity to own a car with potential at a budget-friendly price. Grab a wrench and bring this one back to life!",
