    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly superlative condition. This specimen has been preserved to a showroom standard, exhibiting a flawless exterior luster and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. For the collector or enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality, this vehicle offers a level of refinement and pride of ownership that is increasingly difficult to find on the market today.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
